&lt;h2&gt;About Understood&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Understood is a nonprofit focused on shaping the world for difference. We raise awareness of the challenges and strengths of people who learn and think differently. Our resources help people navigate challenges, gain confidence, and find support and community so they can thrive.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
