&lt;p&gt;To advance Understood’s mission and to further our impact, we’re hiring an Associate Director, Strategic Research &amp;amp; Insights, reporting to our Director of Research. You bring deep experience in management consulting, strategic planning, or client-side insights, and you know how to turn complex market data into clear narratives that inform executive decisions. You brief VPs, represent Understood to external partners and funders, and identify where the market is heading—and where Understood should invest its resources.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid role that requires a minimum of three (3) days a week in our NYC office, with a focus on Monday, Tuesday, and Thursday. We are a Mac-based environment, and team members are provided a Mac laptop for their work.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
