&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Intelligence &amp;amp; Insights:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesize complex market data and competitive intelligence into actionable insights, delivering high-level strategic narratives, SWOT analyses, and clear implications for business decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use market trends and consumer insights to recommend resource allocation and organizational priorities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify “what space” opportunities for growth within the LTD field and adjacent markets by analyzing consumer and product dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advancement Integration:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate directly with the Partnerships, Giving, and Grants teams to provide the high-level market, literature, and competitive research required to establish new funding channels and build credibility with key funders&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;External Research Partnerships:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a principal authority with external clients of Eco’s “Play for Every Brain” universal design research offering; selling, briefing, and delivering research insights that drive impact and resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive impact by briefing partners on high-level research insights and translating complex data into strategic narratives that secure new opportunities and funding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
