&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7-10 years of professional experience, high-level management consulting (e.g., McKinsey, Bain, BCG) or a senior role in strategic planning, market intelligence or client-side insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to deliver insights and counsel to Directors, VPs, and Executive Leadership Teams (ELT).&lt;/li&gt;
